Bulwark.base_description:
For every skill equipped in the Juggernaut branch, gain {ArmorReduction} damage reduction to armor plates.
{ComputedArmorReduction}

Total damage reduction cannot exceed {MaxArmorReduction}.

Bulwark.aced_description:
For each point of Trauma on your current armor plate, gain {AcedArmorReduction} damage reduction for every skill equipped in the Juggernaut branch.
{ComputedAcedArmorReduction}

Trauma is 'permanent' damage that cannot regenerate unless repaired or replaced by an Armor Bag.

ARProficiency.base_description:
For every skill equipped in the Commando branch, Assault Rifles and LMGs gain {IncreasedArmorPenetration} Armor Penetration.
{ComputedIncreasedArmorPenetration}

Each enemy wears a set number of armor layers. If your Armor Penetration is equal to or higher than that number, attacks damage their health directly. If not, attacks damage their armor layers.

ARProficiency.aced_description:
Assault Rifle and LMG reload speed increases by {AcedIncreasedReloadSpeed} for every skill equipped in the Commando branch.
{ComputedAcedIncreasedReloadSpeed}

This bonus doubles when reloading an empty magazine.

DodgeMaster.base_description:
For every skill equipped in the Ghost branch, gain a permanent {IncreasedDodge} chance to Dodge incoming damage.
{ComputedIncreasedDodge}

Your maximum Dodge chance will cap at {MaxDodgeIncrease}. For each active armor plate, it will decrease by {DodgeArmorChunkReduction}.

DodgeMaster.aced_description:
Standing still for {AcedStillDuration} seconds increases your Dodge chance by {AcedIncreasedDodge} for every skill equipped in the Ghost branch.
{ComputedAcedIncreasedDodge}

Once activated, this boost gradually drops back to <Skill>0%,</> over a period of {AcedDecayDuration} seconds.

DroneOperator.base_description:
The Sentry Turret's heat limit increases by {HeatLimit} for every skill equipped in the Engineer branch.
{ComputedHeatLimit}

Turrets build up heat during combat, and will shut down if overheated. Pick up your turret to cool it off.

HackingExpert.base_description:
Hack cameras to view their CCTV network. Gain {BonusRuntime} Runtime to spend on Black Hat operations.

For every two skills equipped in the Black Hat branch beyond the first, receive {AdditionalRuntime} additional Runtime. You can obtain a maximum of {MaxRuntimeCount} Runtimes.
{ComputedAdditionalRuntime}

PistolExpert.base_description:
For every skill equipped in the Hitman branch, Handguns deal {IncreasedDamage} more damage to unmarked targets, or {IncreasedDamageMarked} more damage to marked targets.
{ComputedIncreasedDamage}
{ComputedIncreasedDamageMarked}

TradingExpert.base_description:
Each hostage you trade counts as {GainHostageCount} additional hostage. For every two skills equipped in the Puppet Master branch beyond the first, that count increases by {AdditionalHostageCount}.
{ComputedAdditionalHostageCount}

Trading hostages can delay a police assault, provide consumables, and free crewmates from custody.

SniperExpert.aced_description:
For each headshot you land with a Marksman rifle, your next shot will deal {AcedIncreasedDamage} more damage.
{ComputedAcedIncreasedDamage}

Missing a shot reduces the total bonus by {AcedDecreasedOutgoingDamage}.

AmmoExpert.aced_description:
Your Ammo Bags restore {AcedExtraCount} additional throwable for every two skills equipped in the Ammo Specialist branch.
{ComputedAcedExtraCount}

Throwables can only be restored up to your maximum carrying capacity, which you may increase through other skills.

FlashbangMaster.base_description:
Enemies affected by your Flashbang Grenades take {IncreasedIncomingDamage} more damage for every skill equipped in the Flashpoint branch.
{ComputedIncreasedIncomingDamage}

If multiple heisters apply this skill to a single enemy, only the highest value will count.
